23:39.674 --> 24:03.917
it's harmful but we've got a lot of other things 
cooking right now that I think are more important

23:39.674 --> 24:03.917
to women such as abortion rights and I totally 
agree with her. I mean, that's been, pornography

24:04.057 --> 24:08.922
has been my area of research for a long time and it's 
an area I care about and feel strongly about. But in

24:11.416 --> 24:24.674
women's day-to-day existence, if we have to 
decide which battles we're going to fight

24:11.416 --> 24:24.674
politically, I'm supportive of now fighting to 
keep freedom of choice in that area first and deal

24:11.416 --> 24:24.674
with the pornography later. I'll still continue 
to work in both areas. How has NOW's platform

24:28.375 --> 24:35.123
